data.description: Nestled in the heart of North Lauderdale, this 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence is an exceptional find with boundless potential. The moment you step inside, you'll be greeted by an open concept layout that effortlessly combines style and functionality. The kitchen, complete with a central island, serves as the centerpiece, making it a hub for culinary creations and gatherings with friends and family.Escape to the expansive backyard where a generously sized pool awaits, promising endless hours of relaxation and outdoor enjoyment. It's a private oasis in your own backyard, perfect for making memories under the Florida sun.This property boasts a converted garage, currently serving as an additional bedroom, adding versatility to the space. Use it to suit your unique needs...
